\id EPH - Zyphe
\h EFESA
\toc1 EFESA KHRISAWBU KHATEI PAUL CAKUA
\toc2 EFESA
\toc3 Efs
\mt1 EFESA
\mt2 KHRISAWBU KHATEI PAUL CAKUA
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Khazing a rei tei Khri Zisu apostol a cangpaw kama Paul tah, Khri Zisu letei zingchuipaw Efesa khuapui mehpathai sahlo khatah ca ka ca kua he.
\p 
\v 2 Kaa Paw Khazing le Abuipaw Zisu Khri taiteipaw ningdonah le thlawlungnah cawh naaning khatah ung ky seh.
\s1 Zisu Khri letei Thlawpaw bonghnang
\p 
\v 3 Kaa Buipaw Zisu Khri a Paw le a Khazing, Khri Zisu letah Thlawpaw lang bonghnang maikaw khatei vaicung bonghnang a ma songtupaw cawh reithai tah ung ky seh.
\v 4 Ama taco a mehmuh letah a pathaipaw le suise a kawh lypaw cang rua pawtah Khri letah khazaw tua hlai taitah kaaning cawh a ma thing.
\v 5 Doná tah Khazing taco a dupaw le a lungtlingnah hratah Zisu Khri thongtah a sawtei leh cang rua pawtah khei a ma rawh pacia thah.
\v 6 Macawtaco, a dopaw a Sawcapaw letah amai lytah a ma pehpaw, arungnawpaw a ningdonah rawng tahei Khazing cawh reithai he peh.
\v 7 Khazing ningdonah a chang thai lypaw rawng takhei a thisai thongtah sua ngethainah le tlangnah cawh Khri letah kaa hmuh.
\v 8 Ma ningdonah cawh singnah le hninah vytei khatah Khazing tah a ma luisopaw a cang.
\v 9 Taico a lungtlingnah hratah Khri letei a tingpaw a dunah biaparuh khah kaaning cawh ma hnisah ka,
\v 10 ma cawh a cai le a ning a va tling tihtah alui le avai letei a ungpaw hming vytei khah lu lukheh a cangpaw Khri a rai lekhei hmingkheh tah pahmo khah a cang.
\p 
\v 11 Ama a khuakhangpaw le a za khykhi ciapaw hratah zezong a dunah le a tingpaw kha a tlahpaw teitah a tuatu taco Khri letah a ma thing.
\v 12 Macawtaco Khri letah hnabeisuinah a hnui tawpaw kaaning sahlo tah Khazing rungnawnah cawh reithai he peh.
\v 13 Taico naaning sahlo zong naaning pachahnah thawngchawbia hmuisui thui he ceh ka, naa zing ning taikhei Khri letah na ung hrah he ceh. A zing ciapaw naaning sahlo cawh Khazing tei na cang he ceh tah hninah tah biakangpaw Thlawpaw Pathai khei Ama leco cakhai tah nang na cang he ceh.
\v 14 Thlawpaw Pathai cawh Khazing tah bia a ma kangpaw ry sahlo khah kaa cy a tah hninah amakhang a cang. Ma cawh Khazing tei a cangpaw sahlo tlangnah ning a tlingnah tai a rungnawnah reithainah a cang.
\s1 Alawngnah le thlawchangnah
\p 
\v 15 Ma rawng tahei, Abuipaw Zisu letei na ngepainah he ceh le mehpathai vytei naa donah pawhe kong ka thui ning ri taikhei,
\v 16 naa cawtah lawngbia hlai heh bang bei neh, ka thlawchangnah maikaw letah ka ca thui paria thlang he.
\v 17 Kaa Buipaw Zisu Khri a Khazing, a rungnaw caipaw Paw tah ama naa hnipase khy nápawtah singnah Thlawpaw le hnipasenah cawh ca pei ky he seh tatah thlaw ka chang tei.
\v 18 Naa lungthing meh a pasing khy nápaw caw zong tah thlaw ka chang, ma cawh a ca y hnohnangpaw he hnabeisuinah khah naa hni khy nápaw cawtah le mehpathai sahlo cy ruapaw ry a rungnaw zia naa hni khy nápaw cawtah a cang.
\v 19 Taico Ama a zingpaw kaaning sahlo kaa caw tei zekhatahmai tah reipakhing khy lypaw a laisuipaw a hmingtuakhynah naa hni khy nápaw caw zong a cang. Ma hmingtuakhynah cawh alai ngeteipaw a thawtlungnah a rai hrenah khatah a lo ka,
\v 20 Khri khah thihnah taitah patho kaw ka, vaicung raang letei a cacang lang letah a tysah ning tei a hmangpaw khah a cang.
\v 21 Thlawpaw lang uhnah vytei le nawhnuinah sahlo le hmingtuakhynah le painah vytei le ming sahpaw vytei cung letah Ama cawh uhtu a cang. Ma cawh atocai caw long tahei cang lytah a va chuh lepaw cai caw zong tah a cang.
\v 22 Taico Khazing tah zezongpui khah a pherai letah chia ka, khrisawbu cawtah zezongpui letah lu cangpaw tah a chia.
\v 23 Khrisawbu cawh Ama a pung, Ama a tlangtlingnah cang ka, Ama tah zezongpui khah kawkih letah a chisah.
\c 2
\s1 Khazing letah hringnah
\p 
\v 1 Khuahlai taco naaning cawh rei naa nge lynah cawtah le, naa suanah cawtah khei thlawpaw letah mehthi na cang he ceh.
\v 2 Khazaw phunglang suanah khah naa zui. Alui le avai kaa letei nawhnuinah a hnuipaw, zinglytu sahlo hrong letei rai a hre leimeipaw thlawpaw khah naa zui tei.
\v 3 Kaaning vytei zong heh khuahlai taco, aaning sahlo hratah kaa za hring hrah. Kaa pikhuipaw ngaisaw phung dunah tei a thokhuipaw chahlynah khah tua he peh ka, suadunah le a pacangnah khah kaa zui lai. Ming hringpaw sahlo hratah Khazing thingaenah aa ing tlang hrahring ka cang he peh.
\v 4 Canghrasala, a ma do tunah cawtah zaangsawnah a chang thai lypaw Khazing taco,
\v 5 rei nge ly rawng tei mehthi kaa cangning tahmai tah Khri leco a ma hringsah, ma cawh ningdoná tei pachah naa cangnah cawtah a cang.
\v 6 Taico Khazing tah Khri khaco ma patho ka, Khri Zisu letah Ama khatah vaicung raang leco a ma tysah hrui,
\v 7 ma heh a va chuh lepaw cai letah zekhatahmai tah reipakhing khy a cang lypaw, a chang thai lypaw a ningdonah Khri Zisu letei kaaning khatah a ningdonah a palangpaw hmuhsah ruapaw cawtah a cang.
\v 8 Zingnah thongtah ningdoná tah pachah naa cang he ceh. Ma cawh naaning taiteipaw cang be, Khazing lahsong a cang,
\v 9 tuasanah rawng tah cang be, macawtaco ahohmai a pachaw khy bei he.
\v 10 Hmingchaw tua rua pawtah Khri Zisu letah sahpaw Khazing kih chuh ka cang he peh. Ma hmingchaw sahlo tua ruapaw taco Khazing tah kaa cawtah a pachia ciapaw khah a cang.
\s1 Khri letah sangkheh
\p 
\v 11 Macawtaco chuakehnah lang tah naaning Gental cawngsaw sahlo, khuahlai tei naa cangnah khah a thui thlang my lo. Naaning cawh, “Cingpa a tai lypaw sahlo,” tatah, “Cingpa a taipaw sahlo,” (mehnung kia tah ngaisaw letei cingpa a taipaw he a cang) tah aa tahpaw na cang he ceh.
\v 12 Ma ning takhei co Khri khatah na chai he ceh. Israel mingphing cangnah letah reipaipaw cang bei he ceh, biakangnah a cangpaw biahrainah lekhei khuachai cang he ceh ka, khazaw lehei Khazing hnui ly le hnabeisuinah hnui lytah naa cang kho.
\v 13 Canghrasala atoheh cawh Khri Zisu letah naaning khuahlai tei langhlaw letah a ungpaw sahlo khah Khri thisai thongtah langne letah chia na cang myca he ceh.
\p 
\v 14 Ama ceingei cawh ka rainah peh, mingphing phinghning khah phingkheh tah a ma tuatu, a pachaichynah tlaipia a chehthlahtu, a caraenah lungrua a chingthlah tu,
\v 15 phungbia khah a phunglang khakhei a pungsaw thih ná tah a hlyde tu a cang. Ama a tingpaw cawh phinghning a cangpaw khah Ama letah a thapaw phingkheh tah papi tei arainah laisá pawtah a cang.
\v 16 Khraws letah a thinah thongtah Khri tah aa pahning co pungkheh tah Khazing letah a raisah he ka, aa caraenahpaw he khah a hlydepah he.
\v 17 Ama cawh a vong ka, langhlaw letah a ungpaw naaning le langne letah a ungpaw aaning sahlo khatah arainah kong thawngchawbia cawh a rei.
\v 18 Ama a thongtah Thlawpaw sangkheh tah Paw khatei a nae khynah khah kaa hnui va veipaw a cang.
\p 
\v 19 Macawtaco naaning cawh raang cangpaw cawngsaw le khuachai cang khawh bei he ceh. Naaning cawh Khazing cawngsaw sahlo khatah raang cawngsaw cang hrui he ceh ka, Khazing ingchungkho cawngsaw na cang hri he ceh.
\v 20 Naaning cawh apostol sahlo le Khazing khuavang sahlo tei ahrangbingpaw cung letah sahpaw ing hratah cang he ceh ka, Khri Zisu ceingei cawh abiapuicaipaw ingki lung khah a cang.
\v 21 Ama leco ing pungpaluh cawh a pato thlu he ka, Abuipaw letah behnah ing pathai pawtah padawchypaw a cang.
\v 22 Taico Khazing tah a Thlawpaw tah a ungsopaw ing cang rua pawtah Ama leco naaning sahlo zong hmingkheh tah bing hruipaw na cang he ceh.
\c 3
\s1 Paul Gental mingphing khatah phungreitu
\p 
\v 1 Ma rawng tahei kama, Paul cawh naaning Gental cawngsaw sahlo naa cawtah Khri Zisu tah rai a pakhing rawng tah thong ka tlahpaw a cang.
\p 
\v 2 Naaning naa cawtah Khazing tah a ningdonah thongtah ma rai heh a pa sia tah cawh naa hni thahpaw a cang.
\v 3 A cui teitah ka cia ciapaw hrakhei ma biaparuh heh apalynah tah a pa hni sahpaw cawh a cang.
\v 4 Mataico ma ca heh naa rei tihtah Khri biaparuh khah zetlua tamaw ka hni tahpaw heh naa hni khy thlang a.
\v 5 A khung ciapaw chai sahlo leco Khazing tah ma heh cawngsaw khatah phy bang beh. Canghrasala atoheh cawh Thlawpaw Pathai tah Khazing mingpathai a cangpaw he apostol sahlo le Khazing khuavang sahlo khatah a phy my ca.
\v 6 Ma biaparuh cawh Thawngchawbia thongtah Gental cawngsaw sahlo cawh Israel cawngsaw sahlo khakhei hmingkheh tah ry cy myca hrah he ka, pungsaw pungkheh letei a caibai hratah cang myca he ka, Khri Zisu letei biakangpaw khah aa hrong myca he.
\p 
\v 7 A hmingtuakhynah thongtah kama khatah pehlaipaw Khazing ningdonah thongtah thawngchawbia a sae tah ka cang.
\v 8 Kama cawh Khazing a cawngsaw vytei letei a nyhnai caipaw navy khei ka nyhnai vy thlang naná teitah Khri rungnah a chang thai lypaw kong thawngchaw khah Gental cawngsaw sahlo khatah rei pawtah le,
\v 9 zezong vytei a papitu Khazing tah cai a khung ciapaw vytei letei a za no thlangpaw biaparuh a raihrenah kong heh ming vytei chingpase rua pawtah ma a ningdonah a cangpaw rai heh a pa peh.
\v 10 A tingaipaw cawh khrisawbu hmang tah Khazing singnah a hlu zia khah vaicung raang letei uhtu sahlo le nawhnuitu sahlo lekhei ato lehei hnisah a dunah caw he tah a cang.
\v 11 Ma rai a hrepaw cawh chaizaw a pachiapaw naning tei hrakhei cang ka, kaa Buipaw Khri Zisu letah a tling sahpaw a cang.
\v 12 Khri letah angepainah kaa hnui cawtah le Ama a thongtah Khazing cawh zalong teitah le raechah teitah pangae a he peh.
\v 13 Macawtaco, naa cawtah a chah nápaw cawtah ruhanah ka ingpaw rawng tahei naa lung dia kheh seh tahpaw heh ka ca ching du he. Ruhanah ka ingpaw cawh naa rungnawnah cawtah a cang.
\s1 Efesa khua cawngsaw cawtah thlawchangnah
\p 
\v 14 Ma rawng tahei Paw Khazing hme letah ka khuh ka panai tei.
\v 15 Ama cawh alui letah le vaicung letei a ingchungkho vytei khah ming a sahtu a cang.
\v 16 Mataico, a laisuinah rungnawpaw le hmingtuakhynah khatah naa chunglang hringnah khah a Thlawpaw tah naa thaw a ca patlung khy nápaw he caw zong tah thlaw ka chang tei,
\v 17 ma pawsui co zingnah thongtah Khri cawh naa lungthing letah a ung paria khy a. Mataico donah letah ung tei, thahrang naa thlah khy nápawtah le,
\v 18 mehpathai vytei kha hmokheh teitah hmingtuakhynah naa hnui khy nápawtah le Khri donah a ky zia le a sy zia, a thu zia le a sang zia naa hni khy nápawtah le,
\v 19 ma donah heh mehnung singthainah tah phah khy be tah naa hni tei, Khazing tlangtlingnah vytei khah naaning letah a chi khy nápawtah zong thlaw ka chang.
\p 
\v 20 Kaa chung letei rai a hrepaw a hmingtuakhynah hratah kaa haepaw vytei le kaa pacangpaw vytei a khunglang tai hming a tua khytu Khazing,
\v 21 ama leco chaizaw tah chai vytei chung tai khrisawbu letah le Khri Zisu letah rungnawnah cawh ung paria thlang ky seh! Amen.
\c 4
\s1 Khri pung letah pung kheh cangnah
\p 
\v 1 Mataico Abuipaw rai rawng tei thong a tlahpaw kama Paul tah Khazing tei a ca y hnohnangpaw he hringzia khatah a tlahpaw hringzia khei hring my lo tahpaw heh ka ca pasy he.
\v 2 A pany la, ningnainá tah chih my lo; naa lung a sy sá la, doná tah pakheh le pakheh a cyhlang my lo.
\v 3 Denah rui tei na khichai pawhe ceh thongtah Thlawpaw tei a pungkhehnah khah thlaw ly rua pawtah a zawng lo leimei my lo.
\v 4 Y naa cangning tei hnabeisuinah sangkheh cawtah y naa cangpaw hrakhei pung pungkheh, Thlawpaw sangkheh,
\v 5 Abui pakheh, zingnah sangkheh le, baptisma cangnah sangkheh suipaw a cang.
\v 6 Khazing pakheh ung ka, Ama cawh kaa zongmingtei Paw, kaaning vytei kaa cung letah a ungpaw le kaaning vytei kaa chung letah rai a hrepaw cang ka, kaaning vytei kaa chung letah a ungpaw a cang.
\p 
\v 7 Canghrasala kaaning pakheh cy khah Khri tah Ama a dunah naning tah ningdonah lahsong a ma peh cy.
\v 8 Capathai letei a ciapaw cawh:
\q1 “Cung lang a kening takhei, sae a tlepaw sahlo he cawh a chuilai he ka, cawngsaw sahlo khah lahsong a peh he,”\x + \xo 4:8 \xt Hlaw 68:18\x*
\m a tah.
\v 9 “Cunglang ke,” tah a silang cawh anai vypaw hminghmaw alui lang a za cung thah tahnah a cang.
\v 10 Ma a za cungpaw khah alui le avai le a khunglang tai pahrang thlu ruapaw takhei vaicung a cung a sangnah caipaw lang a kepaw cawh a cang.
\v 11 Thaikhehpaw sahlo khah apostol cangnah, thaikhehpaw sahlo khah Khazing khuavang cangnah, thaikhehpaw sahlo khah thawngchawbia reitu cangnah le thaikhehpaw sahlo khah pastor le cawngpahtu cangnah a peitu he khah Khri heh a cang hi.
\v 12 Ma heh a rai a hre ruapaw tah Khazing cawngsaw sahlo pachiapaningnah khah a cang, ma pawsui co Khri pung cawh a changchy khy a.
\v 13 Khazing Sawcapaw hnithainah le, angepainah kong letah pung kheh kaa cang thlunah tai le meh puitling cang tah Khri a tlingnah vytei kaa phahnah tai ma heh peizo a cang a.
\p 
\v 14 Taico, tuileh tah a paleh a pathae laipaw nyheh hratah kaaning cawh cang khawh a bei he peh. Kaaning dungkhei pawtah aa zawngpaw he meh ziatai sahlo aa cawngpahnah khah kaa zingpaw cang a be.
\v 15 Doná tah biahmuisui tukhah rei hri he peh ka, khrisawbu lu a cangpaw Khri leco zezongpui letah ka changchy he peh.
\v 16 Ama leco pungpaluh cawh a pato thlu he ka, thahrui tah a peitlesah thlu he ka, pung letei a caibai takhei aaning le aa hre ruapaw rai cacy khah hre he ka, pung cawh donah letah a changchy.
\s1 Khainah sawtei hratah hringnah
\p 
\v 17 Macawtaco ma heh ca ching he neh ka, Abuipaw ming tah bia ka ca patai he. Gental cawngsaw sahlo hratah ung khawh khe lo. Aaning sahlo aa rawhnah cawh a paly a palipaw a cang.
\v 18 Aaning sahlo cawh aa lung mehco ka, Khazing hringnah taitah a chaichy he, zecawtamaw tatah aaning cawh aa lung a khongnah rawng tah hnithainah hnui bei he.
\v 19 Ningzaw hnih khawh be ca he ka, aa ngaisawpaw dunah hohenah lekhei a pei he. Macawtaco a pathai lypaw maikaw lekhei a hmang he ka, tainah caang hnih khawh bei he.
\p 
\v 20 Canghrasala, Khri kong naaning tei naa thuipaw cawh ma hraco a cang tlung be!
\v 21 Zisu Khri letei a ungpaw biahmuisui hrakhei a kong cawh thui he ceh ka, Ama leco cawngpah naa cang kho.
\v 22 Macawtaco, naa hringzia a paringpaw kong letah, dungkhei dunah tei a papia a paluipaw, naa cawngsaw cangnah paringpaw khah pahluhly la,
\v 23 naa lungpuh ningcang khah a thapaw tah tua la;
\v 24 dingnah le pathainah hmuisuipaw letah Khazing kha a lo pawtei tua naa cangnahpaw naa cawngsaw cangnah thapaw khah a hrei my lo.
\p 
\v 25 Macawtaco dinglynah khah pahluhly la, pungkheh letei a peitlepaw kaa cang cy cawtah hei naa ingpaw cacy khah biahmuisui ching my lo.
\v 26 “Na thing a ae tahmai tah suanah tua kheh.”\x + \xo 4:26 \xt Hlaw 4:4\x* Na thingaenah cawh ning tlahsah khui kheh la,
\v 27 Setan khah a daw nápaw hminghmaw pei kheh.
\v 28 Aa ru teipaw cawh ru khawh kheh seh la, a phahlahpaw sahlo pehlai khy hra pawtah ama a kih ceingei tah a chahnaipaw rai khah hre hri seh.
\p 
\v 29 Biachaw ly khah naa kaw taitah papia khe la, ahianah hratah male a tua hry khypaw bia, nawthliatu cawtah a chahnaipaw tukhah papia hri my lo.
\v 30 Taico Khazing Thlawpaw Pathai khah a nge chiasah khe lo. Tlangnah ning cawtah Ama khei cakhai naa cang kho.
\v 31 Chiahrunah vytei, thingchia le thingae, male kha a hrychae lai, male thai pachianah le chahlynah a cangpaw maikaw khah vathlang thlu my lo.
\v 32 Pakheh le pakheh zawngrawhnah hnui la, kong a pacang my lo. Khri thongtah Khazing tah a ca ngethai pawhe hratah pakheh le pakheh a ngethai my lo.
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 Macawtaco Khazing dopaw sawtei naa cang cawtah Khazing a ziaza khah a lah my lo.
\v 2 Khri tah ma do katei kaa cawtah a hringnah khah ringthopaw pehlainah le athuihlainah tah Khazing kha a pehpaw hratah donah hringzia khei hring my lo.
\p 
\v 3 Canghrasala, naa hrong letah canu capaw suanah le a pialuipaw a cangpaw maikaw le duhlui dunah tahpaw sahlo cawh a thlang tahmai alai ruapaw cang be. Zecawtamaw tatah ma sahlo cawh Khazing a mehpathai sahlo khaco a tlah be.
\v 4 Biapia bialui, a huaha lypaw bia le siasing palui biarei zong naaning kha a tlah be. Ma navy co Khazing khatah lawngbia rei hri my lo.
\v 5 Mataico ma heh hnih my lo. Canu capaw suanah le a pialuipaw le duhlui a dupaw cawngsaw (Ma hapaw cawngsaw cawh nono a behpaw a cang) taco Khazing le Khri painah raang letah ry cy ruapaw zehmai hnui be.
\v 6 A longpaw bia tah ahohmai a dungkheisah khe lo, ma hapaw hming rawng tahei rei a nge lypaw ma cawngsaw sahlo cung leco Khazing thingaenah cawh a tlung hi.
\v 7 Macawtaco aaning sahlo khaco a pahlawh khe lo.
\p 
\v 8 Khuahlai taco muinah letah ung he ceh ka, canghrasala atoheh cawh Abuipaw letah khainah letah na ung myca he ceh. Macawtaco khainah letei a ungpaw sahlo hratah hring hri my lo.
\v 9 Khainah a thuisu cawh chahnah vytei, dingnah vytei le biahmuisui vytei a cang he.
\v 10 Abuipaw lung a tongpaw hming tukhah hni a pachia my lo.
\v 11 Muinah letei a tlawnglaipaw cawngsaw sahlo tei, aa tuapaw thui le su a hnui lypaw lekhei a pahlawh hrah khe la, chahlynah aa tuapaw tukhah hnisah kaw hri my lo.
\v 12 Bia a nge lypaw sahlo tei aparuh teitah aa tuapaw hming sahlo kong reilai hmai heh ningzaw a chuipaw a cang.
\v 13 Canghrasala khainah tei a palangpaw maikaw cawh hmuh thlu a cang a,
\v 14 zecawtamaw tatah zezong vytei hmuh khypaw tei a tuapaw cawh khainah heh a cang. Macawtaco ma hrahei reipaw a cang,
\q1 “Vy a ihningpaw, a hrah myca la,
\q2 thihnah taitah tho myca,
\q1 Khri tah na cung letah a ca khaiso a,”
\m tahpaw heh.
\p 
\v 15 Macawtaco naa hringzia lekhei a raering ngetei tua o, mehruh hratah ung khe la, mehsing hratah ung my lo,
\v 16 caichaw naa hmuhpaw maikaw khah achaw teitah hmang a zawng my lo, zecawtamaw tatah atotei kaa cai heh caichia a cang hi.
\v 17 Macawtaco hruh khe la, Abuipaw dunah zemaw a cang tahpaw tukhah hni a zong hri my lo.
\v 18 Hringzia a rawhrang khypaw zu khah rui khe la, Thlawpaw tu tah chih hri my lo.
\v 19 Reithainah hlaw le Khazing hlaw le Thlawpaw hlaw tahpaw sahlo khei pakheh le pakheh thawzaang a pei la, naa lungthing vytei khei Abuipaw reithainah hlaw khah sah my lo.
\v 20 Kaa Buipaw Zisu Khri a ming tah zezong vytei letah Paw Khazing khaco alawngnah bia hlai paria thlang my lo.
\p 
\v 21 Khri aa cizawpaw naa cang cawtah pakheh le pakheh naa rai a daw my lo.
\s1 Nupui le pasae
\p 
\v 22 Naaning nupui sahlo, Abuipaw a rai na dawpaw hra he ceh tah, naa pasae leh aa rai a daw my lo.
\v 23 Zecawtamaw tatah Khri cawh Ama a pung a cangpaw khrisawbu lu a cangpaw hratah pasae cawh a nupui lu a cang. Khri cawh khrisawbu a Pachahtu a cang.
\v 24 Macawtaco khrisawbu tah Khri rai a dawpaw hratah nupui sahlo taco pasae leh khah zezongpui letah aa rai a daw hrah he seh.
\p 
\v 25 Naaning pasae sahlo, Khri tah khrisawbu do katei, a cawtah a hringnah a pehpaw hrakhei naa nupui leh khah do my lo.
\v 26 Khrisawbu cawh pathai sá pawtah bia khah hmang tah tui tah a pathaisah.
\v 27 Ma hratei a tuapaw cawh reipachianah le suisepaw a unglypaw le a pathaipaw, ange cangpaw khrisawbu khah Ama lilaw khatah peh a du cawtah a cang.
\v 28 Ma hraco pasae leh taco aaning aa pung aa dopaw hratah aa nupui leh khah aa do ruapaw he a cang. A nupui a dopaw cawh ama le ama a dopaw a cang.
\v 29 Zecawtamaw tatah ahotahmai a pung cawh a hua bang be, Khri tah khrisawbu mingkai katei, a congpaw hratah mingkai ka, a cong hri.
\v 30 Kaaning cawh ama a pung letei a caibai sahlo khah ka cang he peh.
\v 31 “Capaw tah a no le a paw khah seisai he ka, a nupui khah a hlawng a, taico aa pahning co ngaisaw pungkheh tah aa cang a,”\x + \xo 5:31 \xt Atho 2:24\x* a tahpaw khah ma rawng tahei a cang.
\v 32 Ma heh a thuhpaw biaparuh cang ka, canghrasala kama taco Khri le khrisawbu kong ka rei.
\v 33 Ma duitei cawh naaning vytei tah naa pung naa dopaw hratah naa nupui leh zong naa do hrahringpaw he a cang. Nupui taco, a pasae khah a cizaw hrahringpaw a cang.
\c 6
\s1 Sawtei leh le no le paw kong
\p 
\v 1 Naaning sawtei a cangpaw sahlo, naa no naa paw aa reinge my lo, ma cawh Abuipaw dupaw a cang. Zecawtamaw tatah no le paw reinge cawh ahmangpaw a cang.
\v 2 “Na no le na paw cizaw my lo,” tahpaw cawh biakangnah kha a peitlepaw biapeh a hmetaw caipaw a cang.
\v 3 Ma bia cawh naa nge caco, “Naa cawtah chah ka, aluicung lehei naa hringkhua a sy a.”\x + \xo 6:3 \xt Biary 5:16\x*
\p 
\v 4 Naaning paw sahlo, naa sawtei leh khah aa thingaesah khe lo; Abuipaw cawngpahnah le chinghringnah tukhei changchysah hri my lo.
\s1 Sae le abui sahlo
\p 
\v 5 Naaning sae sahlo, alui letei naa bui leh khah Khri a rei naa ngepaw hrakhei cizawnah le thinglung hmuisui teitah aa reinge my lo.
\v 6 Aa mehmuh letah pachaw naa cang nápaw cawtah longlong aa rei cawh nge khe la, Khri sae a cangpaw sahlo tei Khazing dunah aa tuapaw hratah naa lung hmuisui tah tua my lo.
\v 7 Cawngsaw rai cang be, Abuipaw rai a cang tatah lungtho teitah hre my lo.
\v 8 Zecawtamaw tatah Abuipaw taco cawngsaw maikaw khah sae a cang zong, a zalongpaw a cang zong chahnah aa tuapaw naning tei hrakhei longmai a pae he tahpaw cawh naa hni.
\p 
\v 9 Taico naaning abui sahlo, ma hraco naa sae sahlo khah mingkai la, pachih parong khe lo. Aaning kha, naaning kha naa phuhning cawtah Bui a cangpaw Abuipaw cawh vaicung letah ung ka, ahohmai du le hua patlia be tahpaw khah hnih my lo.
\s1 Khazing raedynah chaichi
\p 
\v 10 A changnah letah co Abuipaw le a hmingtuakhynah thawtlungnah letah a cy pawtah ung my lo.
\v 11 Khazing a raedynah chaichi a tlingpaw khah a hrei la, ma pawsui co Setan reipasawhnah le dungkheinah khah naa dawcakhai khy he ceh.
\v 12 Zecawtamaw tatah Kaaning tei kaa dypaw carae cawh thi le saw khatah a cangpaw khah cang lytah uhtu sahlo, nawhnuinah sahlo, ma khazaw muinah hmingtuakhynah le cung lang letei a ungpaw thlawpaw pialuipaw thawtlungnah sahlo khah kaa dy hripaw a cang hi.
\v 13 Macawtaco Khazing a raedynah chaichi a tlingpaw cawh a hrei la, ma pawsui co ning achaw lypaw a va chua tihtah a dawcakhai khy he ceh ka, zezongpui naa tua khy tai zong tah na daw paria khy thlang he ceh.
\v 14 Mataico cyky tah a daw la, biahmuisui tesong khah naa te letah a song my lo. Mataico naa cacanghnaw a pachawngkhainah pho cawtah khei dingnah khah a lah la,
\v 15 arainah thawngchawbia taitah a va chuhpaw a maipacianah khah naa phe letah a pakong my lo.
\v 16 Ma vytei taihei zingnah khah pho cawtah khei a lah la, ma pawsui co mehchaw lypaw Setan tei a ca kawnah pawhe melui hratah a cangpaw caitai khah naa chaiseh khy a.
\v 17 Lukhu cawtah pachahnah khah a khu la, Thlawpaw zyzi a cangpaw Khazing bia khah a lah my lo.
\v 18 Taico, zezong maikaw letah nawpawnah le thlawchangnah a phingphing khei Thlawpaw letah thlawchang my lo. Ma lungpho hmo co a hrah la, mehpathai vytei cawtah thlawchang paria my lo.
\p 
\v 19 Bia ka rei tihtah Khazing tah ka hmokaw a pa hmang nápaw cawtah le thawngchawbia biaparuh cawh cinah hnui lytah ka reilai khy nápawtah ka cawtah thlawchang my lo.
\v 20 Zecawtamaw tatah bahrairui chi tei thawngchawbia aly lang a seipaw ka cangpaw cawh ma cawpaw tahei a cang hi. Ka rei ruapaw khah ci lytah ka rei khy nápawtah ka cawtah thlawchang my lo.
\s1 A changnah kihtlenah
\p 
\v 21 Duchuipaw uny le Abuipaw a sae zingchuipaw a cangpaw Taikhika tah zezongpui khah a ca ching tae he a, ma pawsui co ka tuapaw le ka chuacangnah khah naaning sahlo zong tah naa hnithai a.
\v 22 Ka konglang naa hnithai nápawtah le thawzaang ca pei na he seh tah cawpaw tah ama heh naaning kha ka va thlawpaw a cang hi.
\p 
\v 23 Paw Khazing le Abuipaw Zisu Khri taitei zingnah khatah a cangpaw donah le thlawlungnah cawh uny a cangpaw naaning sahlo khatah ung ky seh.
\v 24 A chang thai lypaw doná tei kaa Buipaw Zisu Khri a dopaw sahlo naa cung letah Khazing ningdonah cawh ung ky seh.
